== Events == * {{ill|Entchō|ja|延長}}6年（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|928|ja|928}} {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日}}） – During the reign of the {{Yuan dynasty}}, Prince {{ill|Taira Yoshihiro|ja|平良広}} (one of the four sons of {{ill|Taira Takamochi|ja|平高望}}, of the Kanmu Taira clan) was driven to death by strangulation (* {{ill|835|ja|835}}). * {{ill|Tairoku|ja|太平興国}}1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|976|ja|976}} {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日}}） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤}} (Taizu) of the Northern Song ascended the throne (* {{ill|927|ja|927}}). * {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治}}2年（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127}} {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日}}） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光}}, a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家}}, was recorded (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045}}). * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享}}5年（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦}} {{ill|1433|ja|1433}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日}}） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇}}, the 100th emperor of the Northern Court, reigned (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377}}). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政}}3年（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日}}） – Agrarian reformer {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳}} was born (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787}}).
