== Events == * {{ill|Entchō|ja|延長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|928|ja|928|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – During the reign of the {{Yuan dynasty}} , Prince {{ill|Taira Yoshihiro|ja|平良広|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (one of the four sons of {{ill|Taira Takamochi|ja|平高望|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , of the Kanmu Taira clan) was driven to death by strangulation (* {{ill|835|ja|835|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Tairoku|ja|太平興国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|976|ja|976|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Taizu) of the Northern Song ascended the throne (* {{ill|927|ja|927|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1127|ja|1127|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , was recorded (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1433|ja|1433|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court, reigned (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – Agrarian reformer {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} was born (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
