* {{ill|Entchō|ja|延長|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|928|ja|928|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|December 4|ja|12月4日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – During the reign of the {{Yuan dynasty}} , Prince {{ill|Taira Yoshihiro|ja|平良広|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  (one of the four sons of {{ill|Taira Takamochi|ja|平高望|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , of the Kanmu Taira clan) was driven to death by strangulation (* {{ill|835|ja|835|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Tairoku|ja|太平興国|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 1st year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|976|ja|976|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 14|ja|11月14日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Zhao Kuangyin|ja|趙匡胤|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  (Taizu) of the Northern Song ascended the throne (* {{ill|927|ja|927|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 2nd year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1127|ja|1127|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 25|ja|11月25日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|ja|源義光|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , a military commander and younger brother of {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義家|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , was recorded (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1433|ja|1433|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court, reigned (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|1856|ja|1856|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ） – Agrarian reformer {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=draft|qq=draft}}  was born (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|qq=draft|qq=draft}} ).

