raft|qq=}} , was recorded (* {{ill|1045|ja|1045|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Eikyō|ja|永享|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 5th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1433|ja|1433|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|December 1|ja|12月1日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Emperor {{ill|Go-Komatsu|ja|後小松天皇|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court, reigned (* {{ill|1377|ja|1377|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|1856|ja|1856|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} {{ill|November 17|ja|11月17日|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ） – Agrarian reformer {{ill|Ninomiya Sontoku|ja|二宮尊徳|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} was born (* {{ill|1787|ja|1787|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=}} ).
