== Events == * {{ill|Entchō|ja|延長|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Entchō|qq=}} 6th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:928|928]] [[:en:December 4|December 4]] ） – During the reign of the {{Yuan dynasty|qq=}} , Prince {{ill|Taira Yoshihiro|ja|平良広|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Taira Yoshihiro|qq=}} (one of the four sons of [[:en:Taira no Takamochi|Taira Takamochi]] , of the Kanmu Taira clan) was driven to death by strangulation (* [[:en:835|835]] ). * {{ill|Tairoku|ja|太平興国|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tairoku|qq=}} 1st year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:976|976]] [[:en:November 14|November 14]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Taizu of Song|Zhao Kuangyin]] (Taizu) of the Northern Song ascended the throne (* [[:en:927|927]] ). * {{ill|Daiji (Japan)|ja|大治|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daiji (Japan)|qq=}} 2nd year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1127|1127]] [[:en:November 25|November 25]] ） – [[:en:Minamoto no Yoshimitsu|Minamoto no Yoshimitsu]] , a military commander and younger brother of [[:en:Minamoto no Yoshiie|Minamoto no Yoshiie]] , was recorded (* [[:en:1045|1045]] ). * [[:en:Eikyō|Eikyō]] 5th year（[[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1433|1433]] [[:en:December 1|December 1]] ） – Emperor [[:en:Emperor Go-Komatsu|Go-Komatsu]] , the 100th emperor of the Northern Court, reigned (* [[:en:1377|1377]] ). * [[:en:Ansei|Ansei]] 3rd year（[[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[:en:1856|1856]] [[:en:November 17|November 17]] ） – Agrarian reformer [[:en:Ninomiya Sontoku|Ninomiya Sontoku]] was born (* [[:en:1787|1787]] ).
